{"tid":1620722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"超市連油都無曬","createTime":"2019-10-04T11:12:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T11:16:12.000Z","uid":72009,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7e07c0fa2e411914fad240962a9b3b0f705f7cd6","tid":1620722,"uid":72009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:12:20.000Z","msg":"港府強推《蒙面法》，社會氣氛風雨欲來，多區有商場表示會提早關門，多區商場於傍晚6時前提早落閘。大批市民在下班後趕到超市購買糧油食物，天后附近超市逾40人排隊結賬，人龍圍繞超市一圈。有OL形容只有打風前夕才會有此現象，批評港府動用《緊急法》，令局勢火上加油，預計未來數日出門不便，故率先購買食物，有超市的蔬菜被搶購一空，儼如戒嚴的氣氛籠罩全港。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />正，攬炒"},{"pid":"708f28e54200b72d3db10a10acc6f0b6714f454c","tid":1620722,"uid":254898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T11:16:12.000Z","msg":"2000 拖到你死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2007 堅持到底<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2014 拉埋入冊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2019 無中生有<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n歷史總是出奇地相似<br />\n本質沒有改變，性質變本加厲<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1620380/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1620380/page/1</a>"}]}